E1FCT3A.translated: ~z~别伤心，哥们。作为新手，你打得够好了。

E1FCT3A.original: E1FCT3_ACT_ARRIVE_POOL_DRUNKA
~z~A drink? Now you're talking my language, brother.
E1FCT3A.translated: ~z~喝两杯？跟我想的一样啊，兄弟。

E1FCT3A.original: ~z~I don't even know why I play this stupid game.
E1FCT3A.translated: ~z~都不知道为啥我会玩这种傻逼游戏。

E1FCT3A.original: ~z~This better be good, man. We're cutting into some serious drinking time here.
E1FCT3A.translated: ~z~希望演出好看点，哥们。待会儿还得在这儿喝上几杯。

E1FCT3A.original: ~z~Glad you could make it, Johnny. We're gonna rule this shit.
E1FCT3A.translated: ~z~真高兴你来了，Johnny。一起尽情放浪吧。

E1FCT3A.original: ~z~Hey Johnny. Let's roll, man.
E1FCT3_ACT_STRIP_LEAVE_DRUNKA
~z~I'm done with this shit, man. You're a lousy fucking date.
E1FCT3A.translated: ~z~我受够了，哥们。跟你出来玩真的烦。

E1FCT3A.original: E1FCT3_ACT_EATERY_LEAVE_DRUNKA
E1FCT3_ACT_DIFF_DRINK_YESA
~z~You seem to have forgotten a key piece of equipment... your fucking bike, bro!
E1FCT3A.translated: ~z~看来你忘了件重要的装备...你丫的车呢，兄弟！

E1FCT3A.original: ~z~A closet man of the arts? Who'd have thought it? Fuck it, I'll watch a show with you.
E1FCT3A.translated: ~z~搞文艺的深柜男？真令人意外啊？妈的，就陪你看一次吧。

E1FCT3A.original: E1FCT3_ACT_ARM_WRESTLING_LEAVE_DRUNKA
E1FCT3_ACT_AIRHOCK_LEAVE_DRAWA
~z~You're crazy, man. We could have cleaned up in there.
E1FCT3A.translated: ~z~你疯了吧，哥们。多看会儿娘们不好吗。

E1FCT3A.original: ~z~Fuck man. I've gotta drain the main vein.
~z~I would have had you if I hadn't got that cramp, Johnny.
E1FCT3A.translated: ~z~要不是我突然抽筋，你就输了，Johnny。

E1FCT3A.original: ~z~That's what happens when you bring your B-game, Klebitz.
E1FCT3A.translated: ~z~谁让你要玩自己不擅长的游戏呢，Klebitz。

E1FCT3A.original: E1FCT3_ACT_HI_LO_CARDS_LEAVE_WONA
~z~Fuck the wheel. Silicone is man's greatest invention.
E1FCT3A.translated: ~z~要啥摩托车啊。硅胶才是人类最伟大的发明。

E1FCT3A.original: ~z~This better not be any of that queer arty bullshit.
~z~Not bad, man. Filled a hole.
~z~Air hockey?! Not quite what I was expecting, brother, I gotta say. But why not...
E1FCT3A.translated: ~z~桌上冰球？！我得说下，跟我想的不太一样，兄弟。但来都来了...

E1FCT3A.original: ~z~You're going down.
E1FCT3_ACT_ARRIVE_PUB_AVERAGEA
~z~This place isn't bad, bro. Just don't eat the peanuts on the bar, if you value your lower intestine.
E1FCT3A.translated: ~z~这地方还不错，兄弟。就是不想闹肚子的话，别吃吧台上的花生。

E1FCT3A.original: ~z~Already? You've gotta be fucking with me, man? We're just getting going.
E1FCT3A.translated: ~z~这么快？你丫存心搞老子吧，哥们？我们才刚要开始。

E1FCT3A.original: ~z~Come on, man. We could at least have finished the game.
E1FCT3A.translated: ~z~别这样啊，哥们。打完这把再走也不迟啊。

E1FCT3A.original: ~z~What the fuck, Johnny? I barely had time to slap an ass.
E1FCT3A.translated: ~z~搞啥啊，Johnny？我都没来得及摸屁股。

E1FCT3A.original: E1FCT3_ACT_ARRIVE_AIRHOCKA
~z~I couldn't even see the numbers, man.
~z~Where's the fucking fire, bro? We could have at least finished the game.
E1FCT3A.translated: ~z~你他妈哪来的火气啊，兄弟？怎么没打完就走了。

E1FCT3A.original: E1FCT3_ACT_LEAVE_PUB_FAVOURITEA
E1FCT3_ACT_ARRIVE_ARM_WRESTLING_DRUNKA
~z~Did you see that last closeout, man? That was some textbook shit right there.
E1FCT3A.translated: ~z~你看到我最后那发绝杀了吗？那可是教科书级别的。

E1FCT3A.original: E1FCT3_ACT_ARM_WRESTLING_LEAVE_LOSTA
~z~I'm going straight for a kebab, man.
E1FCT3_ACT_ARRIVE_STRIPA
~z~Listen man. I'm gonna bail. I can't handle this right now.
E1FCT3A.translated: ~z~听着哥们，我得溜了。我现在吃不消这个。

E1FCT3A.original: ~z~You can't back out on me now. I was about to hit a roll.
E1FCT3A.translated: ~z~你怎么中途逃跑啊。我才刚来感觉。

E1FCT3A.original: E1FCT3_ACT_STRIP_LEAVE_ABANDONEDA
E1FCT3_ACT_DROPOFFA
E1FCT3_ACT_ARRIVE_HI_LO_CARDSA
E1FCT3_ACT_AIRHOCK_LEAVE_ABANDONEDA
~z~Yeah, this'll do. They serve a half-decent whisky in here.
E1FCT3A.translated: ~z~好啊，这家不错。他们家的威士忌还可以。

E1FCT3A.original: ~z~What's your problem, man? We haven't even finished.
E1FCT3A.translated: ~z~你啥毛病，哥们？咱还没打完呢。

E1FCT3A.original: ~z~I thought I had that one in the bag, man, I really did.
E1FCT3A.translated: ~z~我还以为这次我稳了，哥们，真的。

E1FCT3A.original: E1FCT3_ACT_ARM_WRESTLING_LEAVE_WONA
~z~I told you I was good, Johnny.
E1FCT3_ACT_POOL_LEAVE_LOSTA
~z~OK, Johnny. Let's see what you've got.
E1FCT3_ACT_ARRIVE_EATERY_FAVOURITEA
~z~That place sucks, man. Everything tastes like fucking water.
E1FCT3A.translated: ~z~什么傻逼店，哥们。啥酒都淡得跟水一样。

E1FCT3A.original: E1FCT3_ACT_GOHOMEA
~z~This shit's about to go down, bro.
E1FCT3_ACT_LEAVE_EATERY_AVERAGEA
